        "Description": "KING goes on vacation with his wife to Haven Island. He ends up having an affair with Scott Ding Mitchell a pro surfer known around the island for the way he ride dem waves. During  a midnight beach freak off Diego De La Torres a Haven Island staff member catches KING and DING doing it on da beach and confronts them asking KING about his wife. The next day Diego and Scott tell KINGS wife about the affair and they plan on leaking the footage to blackmail KING into runnin dem pockets. HELP KING!!!",
